 Olawale Ajimotokan Armed bandits abducted one person in an early morning attack on Zone A, Anguwan Gade Extension of Kuje Abuja. It was gathered that an 18-year-old foster son of the proprietor of the Supreme Kids Academy, Vctor Egbon was kidnapped in the raid that struck fear and apprehension into the residents. His father, Abdulsalam Ozigi, also suffered seriously injury in the process from machete attack inflicted on him by the assailants. The armed bandits were said to have infiltrated the community at about 12.15 am Monday morning. They invaded the residence of the Ozigis, broke into the family house and then abducted Victor to an unknown destination.Calm had returned to the affected community with everyone going about their lawful business as at the time we visited the community.More to Follow……